{"tid":1120354,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"手機用Leica鏡頭 華為遭五毛狂插","createTime":"2019-04-22T15:06:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T15:54:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"650e02b2b0a53144713b73e57f565d83e659a758","tid":1120354,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T15:06:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190420/20660399\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190420%2F20660399&d=%2BBr8udGLiiUmorY0Hhmb0t6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=a9623b44\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190420%2F20660399&h=fd55abad\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190420/20660399</a><br />\n<br />\n手機用Leica鏡頭 華為遭五毛狂插<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190420/large/a0202a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190420%2Flarge%2Fa0202a.gif&h=e4086c4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王維林以身擋坦克，是六四最重要場景之一。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】內地科技巨企華為先有副董事長孟晚舟於加拿大被捕，後有歐美封殺鋪設5G設備，本已「一身蟻」應接不暇，而在其上月推出旗艦機P30及P30 pro後，其手機鏡頭合作商Leica又被指拍微電影撐六四事件，讓華為再推上風口浪尖。網民也乘勢追擊華為：不取消合作就是賣國賊。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，華為早於2016年已推出首部鏡頭獲Leica認證的手機P9，並於同年與Leica共同開設了開發中心，以研發不同範疇的科技，包括實體光學系統和數碼處理技術等等。數年來，華為已推出P10、P20等一系列以Leica為招徠的手機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：二戰時掌舵人秘密救猶太人<br />\n<br />\n「不取消合作就是賣國賊」<br />\n<br />\n及至上月，華為於法國巴黎公佈P30及P30 Pro系列手機，均獲得法國知名數碼相機畫質評值網DXOMark很高的評分。兩部獲譽為無敵旗艦機所配置的四鏡及10倍變焦鏡頭，都是使用Leica的拍攝系統，但硬件及感光元件則全是Sony的產品。<br />\n<br />\nLeica陷入「六四30周年微電影」風波後，華為也跟着遭殃。有內地網民質疑，Leica是否「反中」，甚至認為，華為是不是要取消與Leica合作，以及停售所有手機產品，否則就是「賣國賊」。<br />\n<br />\nLeica的官方微博，更充滿內地網民痛罵的留言，認為Leica此舉甚為「愚蠢」，令該公司置身於一場公關災難之中，同時連累華為，目前Leica的官方微博已被封。  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n藉攝影師鏡頭重現中共屠城  微電影向坦克人致敬 Leica成敏感字<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n二戰時掌舵人秘密救猶太人<br />\n<br />\n二戰時掌舵人秘密救猶太人<br />\n追尋坦克人 英劇踩中共禁區<br />\n藉攝影師鏡頭重現中共屠城 微電影向坦克人致敬 Leica成敏感字"},{"pid":"bff92129434ae39424270000c96d29a5a2551690","tid":1120354,"uid":2507,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T15:15:55.000Z","msg":"p30好快變禁機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"738c2949088d65631689172506c0cf2aba8c9bf0","tid":1120354,"uid":178317,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T15:18:21.000Z","msg":"快啲躝啦大陸狗,咪污染晒Leica個牌子"},{"pid":"1852ff76b54545b514e25929e92dcb2b350e0e6f","tid":1120354,"uid":119135,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T15:22:34.000Z","msg":"八九六四 三十年<br />\nPeking 30 = p30<br />\n一早已經表明來意"},{"pid":"b292c97c250d6abce934291cedfcf44e5a4574cf","tid":1120354,"uid":119347,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T21:15:49.000Z","msg":"此圖意解為螳臂擋車，即所有外國科技公司係華為面前都只係紙老虎一隻，華為勢如破竹，中國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f147b5ef9912df2755cb058b2fa78a6c3268e46","tid":1120354,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1852ff76b54545b514e25929e92dcb2b350e0e6f","tid":1120354,"uid":119135,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T15:22:34.000Z","msg":"八九六四 三十年<br />\nPeking 30 = p30<br />\n一早已經表明來意"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T16:09:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c53c3d7270e7d95368b6cf4963180c26f1844e3","tid":1120354,"uid":71341,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T21:38:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"00b17321211b68b07d9fe40ab7476c12f926e85e","tid":1120354,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl